author: GameSpot
description:
Silent Hill f has five endings, four of which have completely different boss fights. Here's all of Silent Hill f's endings, full boss fights, post-credit scenes, as well as the UFO ending. Does the infamous shiba inu make an appearance? Watch to find out.

00:00 - Coming Home To Roost
03:14 - Shiromuku fight
15:43 - Fox's Wedding
27:26 - Tsukumogami fight
38:12 - The Fox Wets Its Tail
41:53 - Shiromuku fight 2
46:11 - Shichibi fight
56:55 - Ebisugaoka In Silence
1:02:00 - Fighting the gods
1:18:00 - UFO Ending
title: Silent Hill f - All Endings With Boss Fights
